Locus:
  Case: 26
Title: Baizhang Sitting Alone
---
A monk asked Baizhang, "So what is the peculiar matter?"

Zhang said, "Sitting alone on Great Victory (Daixiong)
summit."

The monk ceremoniously bowed.

Zhang then hit him.
